I'm a peaceful person, I disdain violence & try to do as little harm as possible, I'm a humanist & a vegan but even my love has its limits, I hate bullies. At some point I will snap. I'm very sleep deprived & sick from the stress & their smoking. I can't keep doing this.

Very fortunate for them my kid's dad was here to hold me back & that I'm not quite ready to hurt him to get to their ass. His place is having an electrical repair so he has to stay the night. I haven't had to be restrained in many years. Over a year of cruelty from them though.

I really hope for their sakes they gtfo & very soon cuz I've decided that I'm morally & ethically within my rights to do what needs doing. I've tried everything. No one is going to help us, we can't go elsewhere. I'm stuck here & I can't keep going through abuse & torment.

I'm a man on the edge. I've tried absolutely everything. We're all asking these scumbags for the bare minimum shit on the lease. But they're entitled & violent & threaten us everytime. Bomb threats, burning the house down, threats to jump us. I'm so angry that I'm actually calm..

I will never let someone put a hand on me again, or hurt my child. I'd do whatever it takes and not bat an eye or lose a second of sleep on it if I'm forced to. One of the only things stopping me is scaring my kid who is here and the fact there's no vegan food in prison😊

16 months of hardly sleeping, them having hella squatters maxing out all the hot water, trash everywhere, partying, threats, drugs & chainsmoking in the nonsmoking house making us sick. I have a good trail of my harassment & witnesses. I've given too many chances. I'm not a chump

I try to pacify cuz I've put people that hurt me or loved ones in the hospital, my rage doesn't have an off switch if I get there cuz my abuse. I'm not scared of other people I'm afraid of myself cuz whoever is on the receiving end won't only get their share but what I've held in

I'm not a person that says things I don't mean, I'd never approach someone in a hostile or loud way that I'm not willing to follow through on. I hate a loud bitch that is only brave in a crowd or talks but won't make a move. I don't bluff. I was raised different than that.

All that gardening, baking & cooking to zen out  just to finally have to be held back from fighting that neighbor, I've met my limit, ugly hoe, her mom & sister tried to accost me & the other neighbor cuz they heard us talking about the chainsmoking. Wouldn't get, closer all talk
